sm::eod::io::CodecIDRegistry

CodecIDRegistry Struct Reference

#include <serializablecompressorcodec.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

List of build-in codec id's and codec id ranges. LSB of the codec id is reserved for codec version. MSB is reserved for future use (e.g. category).
